{"title":"Contact Raborn Decision Sciences","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Contact Raborn Decision Sciences","about":{"template":"jolla","image-shape":"rounded","image":"assets/anthony-raborn.jpg","links":[{"icon":"bluesky","text":"Bluesky","href":"https://bsky.app/profile/raborndecisionsciences.com"},{"icon":"github","text":"Github","href":"https://github.com/raborn-decision-sciences"},{"icon":"linkedin","text":"LinkedIn","href":"https://www.linkedin.com/company/raborn-decision-sciences"},{"icon":"envelope-fill","text":"Email","href":"mailto:hello@raborndecisionsciences.com"}]}},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\nHave a measurement, analytics, reporting, or R/Shiny tool problem? Send a short note below.\n\n```{=html}\n<!-- Change or deletion of the name attributes in the input tag will lead to empty values on record submission-->\n<div class=\"rds-contact-form-wrapper\">\n  <form\n    action=\"https://forms.zohopublic.com/anthonyraborndecis1/form/ContactUs/formperma/eRC7sH8Sc7qeaUyjXh69YZaPp4p2K18Q5w6VYqO-62Y/htmlRecords/submit\"\n    name=\"form\"\n    id=\"form\"\n    class=\"rds-contact-form\"\n    method=\"POST\"\n    accept-charset=\"UTF-8\"\n    enctype=\"multipart/form-data\"\n  >\n    <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"zf_referrer_name\" value=\"\">\n    <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"zf_redirect_url\" value=\"\">\n    <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"zc_gad\" value=\"\">\n\n    <div class=\"rds-form-header\">\n      <!--<p class=\"rds-eyebrow\">Contact</p>-->\n      <!--<h2>Contact Raborn Decision Sciences</h2>-->\n      <p>\n        Tell me what you are trying to solve, what tools or data are involved,\n        and what timeline you are working toward.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"rds-form-grid rds-name-grid\">\n      <div class=\"rds-form-field\">\n        <label for=\"Name_First\">\n          First name <span>*</span>\n        </label>\n        <input\n          id=\"Name_First\"\n          type=\"text\"\n          maxlength=\"255\"\n          name=\"Name_First\"\n          fieldType=\"7\"\n          placeholder=\"Your\"\n          required\n        />\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"rds-form-field\">\n        <label for=\"Name_Last\">\n          Last name <span>*</span>\n        </label>\n        <input\n          id=\"Name_Last\"\n          type=\"text\"\n          maxlength=\"255\"\n          name=\"Name_Last\"\n          fieldType=\"7\"\n          placeholder=\"Name\"\n          required\n        />\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"rds-form-field\">\n      <label for=\"Email\">\n        Email <span>*</span>\n      </label>\n      <input\n        id=\"Email\"\n        type=\"email\"\n        maxlength=\"255\"\n        name=\"Email\"\n        value=\"\"\n        fieldType=\"9\"\n        placeholder=\"you@example.com\"\n        required\n      />\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"rds-form-field\">\n      <label for=\"SingleLine\">\n        Organization <span>*</span>\n      </label>\n      <input\n        id=\"SingleLine\"\n        type=\"text\"\n        name=\"SingleLine\"\n        value=\"\"\n        fieldType=\"1\"\n        maxlength=\"255\"\n        placeholder=\"Organization, Self, or N/A\"\n        required\n      />\n      <p class=\"rds-help-text\">\n        If not affiliated with an organization, please put “Self” or “N/A.”\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"rds-form-field\">\n      <label for=\"MultiLine\">\n        What are you trying to solve? <span>*</span>\n      </label>\n      <textarea\n        id=\"MultiLine\"\n        name=\"MultiLine\"\n        maxlength=\"65535\"\n        placeholder=\"Briefly describe the problem, the data/tools involved, and what a successful outcome would look like.\"\n        required\n      ></textarea>\n      <p class=\"rds-help-text\">Please be as descriptive as you can.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"rds-form-grid\">\n      <div class=\"rds-form-field\">\n        <label for=\"Date\">Timeline to start</label>\n        <input\n          id=\"Date\"\n          type=\"text\"\n          name=\"Date\"\n          maxlength=\"25\"\n          placeholder=\"dd-MMM-yyyy\"\n        />\n        <p class=\"rds-help-text\">\n          When would you like to start working on your solution?\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"rds-form-field\">\n        <label for=\"Date1\">Deadline for completion</label>\n        <input\n          id=\"Date1\"\n          type=\"text\"\n          name=\"Date1\"\n          maxlength=\"25\"\n          placeholder=\"dd-MMM-yyyy\"\n        />\n        <p class=\"rds-help-text\">\n          When do you need the project completed?\n        </p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <button type=\"submit\" class=\"rds-submit-button\">\n      Submit inquiry\n    </button>\n  </form>\n</div>\n```\n\nAdditionally, you can contact Raborn Decision Sciences on Bluesky, GitHub, LinkedIn, or via email directly, with all links provided below.\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\nHave a measurement, analytics, reporting, or R/Shiny tool problem? Send a short note below.\n\n```{=html}\n<!-- Change or deletion of the name attributes in the input tag will lead to empty values on record submission-->\n<div class=\"rds-contact-form-wrapper\">\n  <form\n    action=\"https://forms.zohopublic.com/anthonyraborndecis1/form/ContactUs/formperma/eRC7sH8Sc7qeaUyjXh69YZaPp4p2K18Q5w6VYqO-62Y/htmlRecords/submit\"\n    name=\"form\"\n    id=\"form\"\n    class=\"rds-contact-form\"\n    method=\"POST\"\n    accept-charset=\"UTF-8\"\n    enctype=\"multipart/form-data\"\n  >\n    <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"zf_referrer_name\" value=\"\">\n    <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"zf_redirect_url\" value=\"\">\n    <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"zc_gad\" value=\"\">\n\n    <div class=\"rds-form-header\">\n      <!--<p class=\"rds-eyebrow\">Contact</p>-->\n      <!--<h2>Contact Raborn Decision Sciences</h2>-->\n      <p>\n        Tell me what you are trying to solve, what tools or data are involved,\n        and what timeline you are working toward.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"rds-form-grid rds-name-grid\">\n      <div class=\"rds-form-field\">\n        <label for=\"Name_First\">\n          First name <span>*</span>\n        </label>\n        <input\n          id=\"Name_First\"\n          type=\"text\"\n          maxlength=\"255\"\n          name=\"Name_First\"\n          fieldType=\"7\"\n          placeholder=\"Your\"\n          required\n        />\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"rds-form-field\">\n        <label for=\"Name_Last\">\n          Last name <span>*</span>\n        </label>\n        <input\n          id=\"Name_Last\"\n          type=\"text\"\n          maxlength=\"255\"\n          name=\"Name_Last\"\n          fieldType=\"7\"\n          placeholder=\"Name\"\n          required\n        />\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"rds-form-field\">\n      <label for=\"Email\">\n        Email <span>*</span>\n      </label>\n      <input\n        id=\"Email\"\n        type=\"email\"\n        maxlength=\"255\"\n        name=\"Email\"\n        value=\"\"\n        fieldType=\"9\"\n        placeholder=\"you@example.com\"\n        required\n      />\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"rds-form-field\">\n      <label for=\"SingleLine\">\n        Organization <span>*</span>\n      </label>\n      <input\n        id=\"SingleLine\"\n        type=\"text\"\n        name=\"SingleLine\"\n        value=\"\"\n        fieldType=\"1\"\n        maxlength=\"255\"\n        placeholder=\"Organization, Self, or N/A\"\n        required\n      />\n      <p class=\"rds-help-text\">\n        If not affiliated with an organization, please put “Self” or “N/A.”\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"rds-form-field\">\n      <label for=\"MultiLine\">\n        What are you trying to solve? <span>*</span>\n      </label>\n      <textarea\n        id=\"MultiLine\"\n        name=\"MultiLine\"\n        maxlength=\"65535\"\n        placeholder=\"Briefly describe the problem, the data/tools involved, and what a successful outcome would look like.\"\n        required\n      ></textarea>\n      <p class=\"rds-help-text\">Please be as descriptive as you can.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"rds-form-grid\">\n      <div class=\"rds-form-field\">\n        <label for=\"Date\">Timeline to start</label>\n        <input\n          id=\"Date\"\n          type=\"text\"\n          name=\"Date\"\n          maxlength=\"25\"\n          placeholder=\"dd-MMM-yyyy\"\n        />\n        <p class=\"rds-help-text\">\n          When would you like to start working on your solution?\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"rds-form-field\">\n        <label for=\"Date1\">Deadline for completion</label>\n        <input\n          id=\"Date1\"\n          type=\"text\"\n          name=\"Date1\"\n          maxlength=\"25\"\n          placeholder=\"dd-MMM-yyyy\"\n        />\n        <p class=\"rds-help-text\">\n          When do you need the project completed?\n        </p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <button type=\"submit\" class=\"rds-submit-button\">\n      Submit inquiry\n    </button>\n  </form>\n</div>\n```\n\nAdditionally, you can contact Raborn Decision Sciences on Bluesky, GitHub, LinkedIn, or via email directly, with all links provided below.\n"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":"auto","echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"editor":"visual","engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,